{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"10ef442f28","title":"中央文革批转“关于南京大学实现革命大联合的协议”","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"164691f8c9","index":0,"year":1967,"month":12,"day":31,"articleId":"10ef442f28","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"大联合","id":"18bf6a78fe","type":"主题"},{"name":"教育和教育革命","id":"299424f798","type":"主题"},{"name":"红卫兵运动","id":"3be4d5766f","type":"主题"},{"name":"文章","id":"c9f57d6426","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"造反运动和派别斗争","id":"d48f0ea3e8","type":"主题"},{"name":"毛泽东","id":"dd2b275f6c","type":"人物"},{"name":"中共中央批转","id":"ed99218acc","type":"发行机构"},{"name":"中央文件","id":"ef6e778547","type":"文稿大类"},{"name":"中央文革","id":"ef71f03227","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第一版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":"","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"60238a672f","type":"title","text":"中央文革批转“关于南京大学实现革命大联合的协议”","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"10ef442f28","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"2641fd1131","type":"paragraph","text":"中央批示：","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"10ef442f28","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e08e7edd07","type":"paragraph","text":"中央文革小组同意《关于南京大学实现革命大联合的协议》，希望南京大学各派革命群众坚决贯彻执行。","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"10ef442f28","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b51f53e5d4","type":"paragraph","text":"目前，南京大学的革命师生员工应该立即回到本校去，根据毛主席“论教育革命”中所阐明的伟大的无产阶级教育革命思想，复课闹革命。要认真学习和确实执行伟大领袖毛主席的最新指示，加强无产阶级党性，克服资产阶级、小资产阶级派性。在毛泽东思想的原则基础上搞好革命的大批判，搞好革命的大联合和革命的“三结合”，搞好本校的斗、批、改。","index":3,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"10ef442f28","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"1f9829d139","type":"paragraph","text":"要以执行毛主席伟大战略部署的实际行动，来推动南京市和江苏省的革命大联合和革命“三结合\"，夺取无产阶级文化大革命的新胜利。","index":4,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"10ef442f28","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e1d4f03b23","type":"paragraph","text":"中央文革小组","index":5,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"10ef442f28","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"840bc983ce","type":"paragraph","text":"一九六七年十二月三十一日","index":6,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"10ef442f28","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}